name: Sam Korus
tweet: 11/ We believe the auto industry will follow Wright's Law for battery cost declines, but delayed relative to Tesla.

name: Sam Korus
tweet: 10/ Why is this bad for the competition?  Generally prices from Wright's Law can be applied across an entire industry, but Tesla's speed of iteration and degree of verticalization make leaks and learnings harder to apply to other companies.
